text: With two Senate seats, competitive House races, and a legislative majority in the Georgia House at stake, our state is the battleground in the fight for the soul of our democracy. Get ready, Georgia!

Our fight to expand health care coverage, ensure quality education for our children no matter their neighborhood, and protect the dignity of working people will only succeed if it is truly people-driven, which is why I am proud to have Democracy for America's support.Democracy for America is proud to endorse Reverend Raphael Warnock in his U.S. Senate race in Georgia! Rev. Warnock has helped lead the fight for social, racial, & economic justice ever since he began preaching from Dr. King’s pulpit at Ebenezer Baptist Church. In the U.S. Senate, we know he'll continue to fight for an America where every family can thrive.

As young people across Georgia are registering to vote in higher numbers, the electorate is shifting, and so is the face of politics in our state. This is the year we elect leaders who stand up for all Georgians.

My first time visiting Ebenezer was as a student with the TRIO Upward Bound program. Since then, I've dedicated my life to helping others reach their highest potential. I’m here today because members of SAEOPP showed up for me. I’m honored to show up for them today at their annual conference.
Caught up with my friends on V-103 The People's Station this morning. Did you catch us on air?
It's a real honor to have the endorsement of Stacey Abrams. She's a tremendous leader for Georgia and our country. Thank you, Stacey.

Growing up in public housing in Savannah, I learned from my parents the power of faith, love, and hard work. Those values brought me all the way Dr. King’s pulpit at Ebenezer Baptist Church where I now preside as Senior Pastor. I’ve spent my whole life trying to be ready to serve and to help people. But the concerns of Georgians have been ignored by a Washington that cares more about power and profits than the well-being of hard working families. That’s why I’m running for U.S. Senate -- to fight for Georgia families, defend the dignity of working people and to make sure ALL voices are heard. Are you ready? Join us: http://warnockforgeorgia.com/
